The paper deals with face alignment using deep convolutional neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of deep learning models for feature extraction and regression also suggests that the paper could belong to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The evaluation of the proposed method on publicly available datasets also suggests that the paper could belong to multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories.
